snippet.title: Shishi : Timeless Prelude - Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the trailer of Shishi : Timeless Prelude!

Shishi : Timeless Prelude is a colorful dungeon role-playing game. As Elia, a young mage, you will explore the depths of a sacred sanctuary to complete your training to become an Oracle.

Wishlist now : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2215340

#TimelessPrelude #indiegames #gamedev #roguelike
